your dream of apples?

516
00:43:06,851 --> 00:43:09,251
Yes. It's the same boy.

517
00:43:10,355 --> 00:43:12,915
But in the orchard dream
it was a man.

518
00:43:13,024 --> 00:43:16,482
- Can't you make sense of it?
- Would you like me to?

519
00:43:16,594 --> 00:43:20,553
Oh, I would love you to!
I-I-I can't make sense of it.

520
00:43:20,665 --> 00:43:22,530
But, um...

521
00:43:22,633 --> 00:43:25,101
I have a feeling that...

522
00:43:25,169 --> 00:43:28,036
they're all coming
from the same place.

523
00:43:28,106 --> 00:43:29,767
From you?

524
00:43:29,841 --> 00:43:33,368
- No, no! From him.
- And who is he?

525
00:43:33,478 --> 00:43:35,469
I don't know.

526
00:43:35,580 --> 00:43:37,571
But I think he deserves a name.

527
00:43:39,917 --> 00:43:42,579
We'll call him Red.

528
00:43:42,720 --> 00:43:44,585
It's appropriate.

529
00:43:48,192 --> 00:43:50,126
OK, Claire.

530
00:43:50,228 --> 00:43:52,423
Let's leave it there for the moment.

531
00:43:52,530 --> 00:43:55,055
OK. (Sighs )

532
00:43:58,536 --> 00:44:03,030
We're gonna take you to get an ECG
and check your blood pressure.

533
00:44:03,107 --> 00:44:07,476
- Are you gonna keep me here?
- We'll supplement your medication.

534
00:44:07,545 --> 00:44:09,570
Mr Cooper, please come in.

535
00:44:10,815 --> 00:44:12,715
Oh.

536
00:44:14,419 --> 00:44:16,284
Take a seat.

537
00:44:17,955 --> 00:44:20,253
