538
00:44:20,324 --> 00:44:22,383
Here, boy!

539
00:44:25,296 --> 00:44:27,696
Dobie!

540
00:44:27,765 --> 00:44:30,063
- Dobie!
- What?

541
00:44:30,134 --> 00:44:32,898
He's been missing all day.

542
00:44:32,970 --> 00:44:34,870
Oh, great.

543
00:44:34,939 --> 00:44:36,998
How is she?

544
00:44:37,442 --> 00:44:40,309
They want me
to sign her into Stapleton.

545
00:44:40,378 --> 00:44:44,041
I'm sorry.
I feel like it's all my fault.

546
00:44:45,750 --> 00:44:48,218
It's not your fault, Mary.

547
00:44:51,355 --> 00:44:53,220
Dobie!

548
00:44:53,591 --> 00:44:55,422
Dobie!

549
00:44:57,195 --> 00:45:01,097
- (Growling)
- (Man ) Come on. Come on.

550
00:45:01,165 --> 00:45:03,963
Good boy. Good boy.

551
00:45:04,101 --> 00:45:07,502
- (Whimpering)
- Good boy.

552
00:45:24,555 --> 00:45:26,955
(Barking and whimpering)

553
00:45:42,773 --> 00:45:44,866
Dobie?

554
00:45:48,479 --> 00:45:50,947
Dobie, what is it, boy?

555
00:45:51,549 --> 00:45:54,643
- Dobie? What, boy?
