556
00:45:58,823 --> 00:46:00,688
Dobie!

557
00:46:03,661 --> 00:46:07,961
Dobie? Dobie?

558
00:46:09,100 --> 00:46:11,159
Dobie? Dobie?

559
00:46:11,269 --> 00:46:13,999
(Whimpering and barking)

560
00:46:14,071 --> 00:46:16,835
Dobie! Dobie!

561
00:46:20,177 --> 00:46:22,236
