737
01:07:36,886 --> 01:07:40,049
Yeah, maybe. Whatever you wanna do.

738
01:07:52,402 --> 01:07:54,893
(Siren wailing)

739
01:07:54,971 --> 01:07:59,999
- Could we have some music?
- Music? Sure.

740
01:08:03,513 --> 01:08:06,004
( Quiet music)

741
01:08:06,749 --> 01:08:08,580
You work nights.

742
01:08:08,685 --> 01:08:11,586
- Uh, yeah.
- What's your name?

743
01:08:11,654 --> 01:08:16,057
- Vivienne. What's yours?
- Walter.

744
01:08:18,294 --> 01:08:22,321
That's a nice name, Vivienne.
Hey, how you spell that?

745
01:08:22,432 --> 01:08:25,299
V-I-V-I-E-N-N-E.

746
01:08:29,672 --> 01:08:32,539
Can't keep your eyes off me,
can you?

747
01:08:32,642 --> 01:08:35,736
- Off what, Vivienne?
- My legs.

748
01:08:37,714 --> 01:08:40,342
Pity to leave you so soon,
Vivienne.

749
01:08:40,416 --> 01:08:44,512
Well...I'm in no real hurry.

750
01:08:45,622 --> 01:08:49,388
Well, what do you know? Neither am I.

751
01:08:52,762 --> 01:08:56,698
